maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
Sorry, nothing seems to work.
She still doesn't respond.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
Désolé, mais je ne peux rien y faire.
elle ne réagit toujours pas.

maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
I'm not sure. It's possible that
she still perceives her surroundings.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
Je ne suis pas sûr. C'est possible
qu'elle perçoive encore ce qui se passe.

maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
I'm... very sorry.
I tried everything.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
Je... suis désolé.
J'ai vraiment tout essayé.

maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
I honestly have never encountered
an issue like this.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
C'est bien la première fois que
je rencontre un cas comme ça.

maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
It's possible that her past 
experiences have led to this.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
C'est possible qu'un épisode de
sa vie soit responsable de cela.

maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.orig:
That's why... there's one 
last thing we can try.
maps/dreams/fifth.json/entities/0/settin.text:
C'est pourquoi... il y a encore une
chose que l'on peut essayer...
On peut essayer... de la faire tout oublier.

maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.orig:
Sure...
It's supposed to be a long parkour.
maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.text:
Bien sûr...
C'est censé être un long parkour.

maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.orig: It's all about the journey, no?
maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.text: Mais c'est surtout histoire de faire le voyage, non ?
Il faudrait mieux faire durer ça.

maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.orig: Yes, apple trees all over the place.
I suppose I might as well show that place to you.
maps/dreams/first.json/entities/1/settin.text: J'imagine que je pourrais aussi te montrer cet endroit.

maps/dreams/fourth-2.json/entities/161/s.orig: You seem to be caught up in a long dream. Maybe have a look around?
maps/dreams/fourth-2.json/entities/161/s.text:
Vous semblez être coincé dans un rêve qui dure.
Peut-être faut-il jeter un œil aux alentours ?

maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.orig:
It won't be integrated into the 
official playground anytime soon.
maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.text:
Il ne risque pas d'être intégré au
Terrain de Jeu officiel de sitôt.

maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.orig:
Right... There is enough room 
to run some experiments.
maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.text:
Bien... Il y a assez de place
pour faire quelques expériences.
Hm ? Non, Sergey n'est pas là.
Je ne peux pas vraiment lui en vouloir.

maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.orig:
Still... we got this far!
We can't just stop now, can we?
maps/dreams/fourth-3.json/entities/169/s.text:
Mais bon... on est allé si loin !
On ne peut pas s'arrêter maintenant, non ?

maps/dreams/fourth.json/entities/195/set.orig:
Hey, I told you this 
one isn't for everybody.
maps/dreams/fourth.json/entities/195/set.text:
Hé, je te l'avais dit que celui-là
c'était pas donné à tout le monde.

maps/dreams/fourth.json/entities/195/set.orig:
Come on, I don't want 
you to break your fingers.
maps/dreams/fourth.json/entities/195/set.text:
Allez, je n'ai pas envie
que tu te casses les doigts.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig:
Penguins on mountains. 
I'm not kidding.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text:
Des manchots sur des montagnes.
Je déconne pas.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig:
I know. 
They had plenty 
of strange ideas.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text:
Je sais.
Ils avaient plein
d'idées étranges.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig:
Apparently that's what 
people like these days.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text:
Apparemment c'est ce qui plait
aux gens en ce moment.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig: I know, it can be a tad lonely.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text: Je sais, on est un peu seuls.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig: But it's a small price to pay.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text: Mais c'est un petit prix à payer.

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig:
After all... 
we're about to revolutionize 
the entire field!
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text:
Après tout...
on va révolutionner
le domaine entier !

maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.orig:
I'm just glad 
we found somebody
who embraces the potential.
maps/dreams/second.json/entities/119/set.text:
Je suis juste content
que l'on ait trouvé
quelqu'un pour nous aider.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
It makes you wish...\.
you could just stay in this world...
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Parfois on se dit...\.
qu'on aimerait bien pouvoir
rester dans ce monde.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
This world...\.
He gave it to me
to design as I please.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Ce monde...\.
Il me l'a donné,
pour que je le façonne
à ma guise.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
This is what I always 
dreamed about.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
C'est ce dont j'ai
toujours rêvé.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
So why would you 
harbor all these doubts?
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Donc pourquoi est-ce que
maintenant tu as tant de doutes ?

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
Things are just 
fine so far, no?
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Les choses se passent bien
pour le moment, non ?

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig: This is no race against time.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text: Il n'y a aucune course contre le temps.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
I really cannot imagine
how you must feel right now.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Je ne peux pas imaginer
comment tu dois te sentir
en ce moment.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig:
It must feel really strange, hm? 
Seeing me like this.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
Cela doit te faire très étrange, mmm ?
de me voir comme ça.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig: That's why they told me to stay away from you.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text:
C'est pour ça qu'ils m'ont dit
qu'il ne faut pas que l'on se voie.

maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.orig: Because I want you to feel it as well.
maps/dreams/third.json/entities/68/setti.text: Parce que je veux que tu le ressentes aussi.
